When we recite the mantra

224
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,600
we are covered by the big

225
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,600
white umbrella because

226
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,600
we are residing in our home

227
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,600
we are safe and we are sheltered.

228
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,600
That's why the shragama

229
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,600
sutra is called

